Html: Optimizations for prot paladins have been glitched for a couple of days.  Can someone tell me how to roll back to an earlier version of Rawr and/or an earlier version of the Prot Paladin model?

Go to the downloads page.

Look on the right hand side in the iFrame that says "Other Downloads"

Click on the version of Rawr you want.

Select the download package.

Extract/run like normal.
